Cli directly for chat\n- Session keys: bound sessions use telegram:{chatId}, unbound web sessions use web:{sessionId}\n- Safe-to-modify config keys: LOG_LEVEL, REQUEST_TIMEOUT_MS, AI_CLI_HEARTBEAT_MS, MAX_PROMPT_CHARS, MAX_HISTORY_TURNS, SYSTEM_MONITOR_INTERVAL_MS, SESSION_TIMEOUT_MS, TASK_DEBOUNCE_MS\n- ANSI stripping happens in onAssistantChunk hook via ansiProcessChunk() — never strip in final reply path\n- .btn:disabled uses pointer-events: none to prevent hover CSS from firing on disabled buttons\n- .panel and .sub-panel are separate CSS rules (not grouped) to allow different box-shadow depths; shadow colors use rgba derived from --text (#1f2633) for cool-tone palette coordination\n\nUPDATED: 2026-03-23\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":24,"oldLines":5,"newStart":24,"newLines":6,"lines":[" - ANSI stripping happens in onAssistantChunk hook via ansiProcessChunk() — never strip in final reply path"," - .btn:disabled uses pointer-events: none to prevent hover CSS from firing on disabled buttons"," - .panel and .sub-panel are separate CSS rules (not grouped) to allow different box-shadow depths; shadow colors use rgba derived from --text (#1f2633) for cool-tone palette coordination","+- .app-header uses position: sticky + background: var(--bg) + z-index: 10 — always pair sticky with background to prevent content bleed-through; padding-bottom + negative margin-bottom offsets border-bottom from grid gap"," "," UPDATED: 2026-03-23"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
